for loop

Syntax:
for(){
    //block of code 
}

()>>>initilization        >>> Start 
  >>>Condition            >>> End/Stop     || true >> loop runs || false loop terminates              
  >>>Increment/Decrement  >>> Increase/Decrease


for(initilization;Condition;Increment/Decrement){
    //block of code 
}

